<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Donate Now</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/donate.css">
  <link rel="icon" href="/icon.png">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css"
    integrity="sha512-Evv84Mr4kqVGRNSgIGL/F/aIDqQb7xQ2vcrdIwxfjThSH8CSR7PBEakCr51Ck+w+/U6swU2Im1vVX0SVk9ABhg=="
    crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="header-content">
      <h1>Donate Now <i class="fa-solid fa-hand-holding-medical"></i></h1>
      <p>Support our efforts to improve healthcare services in rural areas. Every contribution matters.</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="donate-now">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="donate-content">
        <h2>Your Contribution Can Make a Difference <i class="fa-solid fa-hands-holding"></i></h2>
        <p>Help us bridge the healthcare gap by donating to our cause. Your generosity allows us to provide essential services like medical checkups, medicines, and educational programs in rural areas.</p>
        
      <div class="qr-code">
        <h3>Scan to Donate <i class="fa-solid fa-qrcode"></i></h3>
        <img src="qr.png" alt="QR Code">
        <p>Use any QR code scanner to make a quick donation. </p>
        <p>Scan this QR code to make payments via UPI, Paytm, PhonePe, or Google Pay. Fast, secure, and hassle-free transactions!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <p>&copy; 2025 Healthcare+. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
